## Configuration

Llamero uses `pyproject.toml` for configuration:

```toml
[
tool.readme.tree
]
# Configure files to ignore in project tree
ignore_patterns = [
    "__pycache__",
    "*.pyc",
    ".git",
    ".venv",
    # Add custom patterns...
]

[
tool.readme.sections.order
]
# Configure README section ordering
"introduction.md.j2" = 0
"prerequisites.md.j2" = 1
"usage.md.j2" = 2
# Add custom sections...
```
